title: Taylor Swift to perform at Hamilton Island: Nova
text: Taylor Swift to perform at Hamilton Island: Nova Shakira Sellen | 26th Oct 2015 10:56 AM Shakira Sellen Journalist I moved to Mackay in 2011 and haven’t looked back since. I’ve grown to enjoy the laidback Mackay lifestyle and all it has to offer. Over the years I have also spent time visiting the Whitsundays and my favourite place to date would be Whitehaven Beach. Being on the go all the time in a fast-paced job I also can’t go past a good cup of coffee. When it comes to writing, I love to meet residents in the community and find about their life as I feel everyone has an interesting story to tell.
